> **For Claude:** REQUIRED SUB-SKILL: Use superpowers:executing-plans to implement this plan task-by-task.

**Goal:** Fix all Important + Minor findings from the post-increment-7 code review: tz format guard, orchestrator consistency, per-call timeouts, transit CSS, response field allow-listing, contract test resilience, static file error, and InputPage UX.

**Architecture:** Purely defensive — no new features, no API changes. All fixes are local within existing files. Test-first for anything testable. Minor findings that need no test get a direct fix + commit.

**Tech Stack:** Node.js ESM, `node:test` / `node:assert/strict`, Vanilla JS frontend.

