## What we're fixing

| ID | Severity | File | Finding |
|----|----------|------|---------|
| I1 | Important | `server.js:508-509` | `orchestrateDailyExperience` uses `?? 0` and misses `location.latitude` alias |
| I2 | Important | `server.js:499-526` | Shared AbortController — slow bootstrap eats daily's timeout budget |
| I3 | Important | `server.js:198-200` | `tz` validation accepts any non-empty string, no format guard |
| I4 | Important | `TransitCalendarPage.js:103-106` | API number injected into inline `style` attribute |
